messages.content: If you'll be around, maybe I'll come over around noon on Saturday
Ok well we should be around regardless! Just let me know when works for you best
I actually work Saturday evening. What about Sunday? Or else sometime before 3 on Saturday
That would be great Andy!! We should be here this weekend. Let me see if the Murts will be around so you can see them too. How does Saturday for dinner sound?

Taylor, I realized it's been a while since I seen you and Lily and Cara, and I think we live right next to each other. Let me know if there's a time I could at least stop by, maybe this weekend. If you're busy, no problem. Hope y'all are doing well. Andy
